Zanzibar President, Hussein Mwinyi on Tuesday sworn- in Othman Masoud Othman as First Vice President of Zanzibar, during the ceremony held at the state house in Zanzibar. Masoud's appointment comes weeks after the death of First Vice President Seif Sharif Hamad in Dar es salaam on FebruaryÂ  17, this year. He was the ACT-Wazaledo national chairman. The outspoken former Zanzibar Attorney General has pledged to follow his predecessor's footsteps to help enhance unity, peace and political tolerance in the semi-autonomous Island.